{
  "stem": "7017.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was Dyhernfurth, Breslau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was wearing-- when I was working in Dyhernfurth in concentration camp-- I was wearing shoes, Holland shoes, from wood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if you didn't have enough food to eat, your feet-- I got swollen up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I figure, I have no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's two ways.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I'll be-- if I not going over there, it just would kill me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would not be able to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other chance I got, if I go to the [NON-ENGLISH], they will mark my number that I got on my hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After a couple of months, so many people goes to [NON-ENGLISH], they mark down-- write your number.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they got enough people, they take them away to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew this before, but I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "See, this time-- if you're in a situation like this, you don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I decided I go in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went in the [NON-ENGLISH], the little hospital. 10 days I was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I came out a new person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I  was able to work and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took my number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I know what they marked down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After two, three months later, they called my number out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't call us by names, just by the number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, you have to be-- there's this place, upper place-- the trucks will be there, and you have to go away with the trucks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, in the morning I went down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were other people before that went to work at 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told me I should give them the jacket and the things that I eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The part, I don't know what they called it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
